                                <title>Two sermons for the feast of Purim, in Arabic</title>
                                <note/> 
                                <msItem xml:id="MS_Heb_f_24-item1-item1" n="a">
                        <p>beg. missing; ends <quote type="end">וכמא קאל קומי אורי ... וכן יהי רצון</quote>.</p>
                                <p>The copy was finished on the <date calendar="Hebrew-Seleucid" when="1481">10th of Adar, 1481 Sel.</date> = <date calendar="Gregorian" when="1170">1170 A.D.</date>, by <persName>Manasseh, son of R. Eleazar</persName>;</p>
                     </msItem> 
                                <msItem xml:id="MS_Heb_f_24-item1-item2" n="b">
                        <p>(<locus from="9a">fol. 9</locus>) beg. and end missing.</p>
